{"tid":1545604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 幫手推#adore#機場旅行攻略","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:19:04.000Z","uid":71624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e41c91f761f02e77639f5bbbab3ccf52e207701","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"嚟緊星期六就係和理飛<br />\n準備出發去旅行嘅巴打， 喺呢度為你準備一個簡單而清晰嘅旅行攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出發前準備</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 小型行李喼或背囊， 三至四件衣物 ，少量糧食及清水<br />\n2. 一張電子機票， 不論真假， 留意當日航班編號及時間， 首選2至6時的航班<br />\n3. 護照<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出發當日</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">請準時</span>一點正到達機場， 自己預返車程所需時間<br />\n2. 不戴口罩<br />\n3. 切勿帶任何裝備， 以免被懷疑係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 切勿穿黑衣<br />\n5. 有車嘅巴打請揸車 ，冇車嘅巴打請搭巴士， 不建議搭機鐵， 因為落車地點同巴士私家車唔一樣（ <span style=\"color: red;\">巴士同私家車落車地點就喺登機大堂門口</span>）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>到達機場後</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 耐心在<span style=\"color: red;\">登機大堂</span>門口排隊， 請遵守秩序一個接一個<br />\n2. 唔好叫口號<br />\n3. 唔好派傳單<br />\n4. 成功進入機場後， 可以出返嚟，再重新排隊， 但唔好排返同一個入口， 除非你知道嗰個保安係自己友<br />\n5. 如果被拒絕進入機場， 請去另一個入口， 再次耐心排隊<br />\n6. 唔好破壞公物， 唔單止無意思，仲會破壞成個旅行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有動物出沒時</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 請保持冷靜， 你哋係遊客， 唔使理佢哋<br />\n2. 假如被盤問， 請冷靜回答你點解要嚟機場（有巴打提供咗一百個理由）<br />\n3. 假如被搜查， 請合作，咪畀啲衣物，食物同護照佢睇<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">唔好撩佢</span>， 你撩佢，即係叫佢過嚟捉你， 到時其他人又忍唔住要救你， 唔好一時意氣累街坊， 破壞成個旅行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當聽到宣布機場疏散/關閉</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 請勿驚慌， 唔好又重複上次嘅錯<br />\n2. 請同遊客一齊疏散， 簡單嚟講就係跟大隊 去搭巴士走<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">遊客疏散曬，啲飛機自然會停飛</span>，唔好傻豬豬自己留喺機場俾動物打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>旅行攻略重點</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">完全遊客look</span>，分唔到邊個係真<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">冇破壞，冇口號 ，冇示威</span>， 何來非法集會<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">請準時，請準時，請準時</span>， 因為很重要所以要講三次<br />\n4. 帶定零食又好，遊戲機又好，去慢慢排隊，慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢度派下定心丸</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 過往三次去旅行， 冇放過一次催淚彈， 最近動物收斂咗， 而且機場唔適合放催淚彈， 又有旅客， 就算有動物都唔會有催淚彈<br />\n2. 如果佢哋亂打人， 咁難免會打中星加坡韓國日本或者台灣馬來西亞嘅遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 如果要濫捕， 都搵唔到罪名可以屈<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\n最後，有興趣可以睇返之前嘅分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[必看] 機場活動分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532668\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532668</a>"},{"pid":"579e7cd77041f87cad768cd7285484ff02b189ca","tid":1545604,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"831太子嘅post有啲似當初不斷下沉嘅機場post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545597</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae856413f764836c2eb7111e4b0c76a6ff2a73d5","tid":1545604,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e133b110d441ab31aff0c1ea00c5e1ef6ae779c","tid":1545604,"uid":71233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e36ae336dafb77d65541c96cf31164cbcea41a65","tid":1545604,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=2126c5bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"286b93b07a8656f5cebafdc14069708bc43ccf9d","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f641f536855f54ee5b70dcb450ec58d7d1951dc","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"552f121d89b6f25a7c3c6985d7417f907e8b1205","tid":1545604,"uid":35151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"76fc5c7f6fe50d1b46e64e810c7e80d00730afcb","tid":1545604,"uid":269226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"9月7號 齊齊入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f3cc81cf60b3ffab7f5d255546d0e2718f3386","tid":1545604,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"credit to <span style=\"color: red;\">你把我灌腸巴打</span><br />\n太有用幫佢copy and paste<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士撚here<br />\n雖然我係P牌仔，<br />\n但利申我係巴士公司做左幾年駐守機場<br />\n首先入柏麗灣係無用既，最多都係塞到馬灣<br />\n因為柏麗灣巴士只經青馬大橋但唔經收費站<br />\n如果想塞青馬收費站<br />\n<br />\n揸車組：瘋狂揸車出入青馬比金牛佢找錢，<br />\n或者過收費站個陣狂玩野e.g. 係咁摷錢、喪問野、全數比晒毫子 etc.<br />\n<br />\n搭車組：青馬收費站有條循環線入迪士尼叫 R8<br />\n呢條線係 迪士尼開，經迪欣湖，之後去青馬收費站(北行)，再過橋U turn返青馬收費站(南行)，然後又返迪欣湖同迪士尼，全程唔落車都係收$7<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想搭呢條R8都無問題，<br />\n可以搭任何一架E線/A線巴士，<br />\n去到青馬收費站(南行)落車，<br />\n再用行人隧道過對面青馬收費站(北行)搭返出市區<br />\n提提各位：城巴A線用八達通比錢，即日回程個程車係有半價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而E線最平果3條線都係 $10.8 分別係<br />\nE31 荃灣愉景新城 &lt;&gt; 逸東邨<br />\nE32 葵芳南 &lt;&gt; 機場博覽館<br />\nE32A 葵芳南 &lt;&gt; 東涌碼頭 (經:荃灣)<br />\n<br />\n而勇武組就自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果勇武rb塞青馬收費站似乎唔太可行<br />\n因為狗可以即時去果個位清場<br />\n可能手足未塞晒個陣警畜已經出左黎<br />\n同埋如果有手足要走先，<br />\n封左路就需要行返欣澳站搭鐵走<br />\n或者欣澳站搭去愉景灣轉船走<br />\n<br />\n仲有澄清返其實901個日大部份人都係搭巴士入去機場<br />\n因為黨鐵機場一出根本就入唔到T1甚至出唔到機場巴士總站<br />\n全靠勇武衝爆左機鐵站手足先入到去<br />\n總之屯門至赤鱲角隧道未通車之前，<br />\n青馬收費站就係機場既春袋，<br />\n2015年有船hi到青馬大橋搞到封橋，<br />\n成個大嶼山同機場即變荒島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3fad50a870dae7a2dfdd219464d361df51055d","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"602d567de42594a312b789627039cbb92a97a469","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e3ebe06b34e41de0c1c05cace32f1d68cb59067","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"8a6c18befd4b247b68f9f0f6d7cb7cb4ab364669","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fb6cf8f018555d771e98517e42eaa3c06de070e","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7248f57b0606299eab23dba79de1d980d0f8a59d","tid":1545604,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}